OL,7,FHealth unions have warned that
OL,8,F"patients being cared for in corridors
OL,9,Fis not what our members signed up for".
OL,11,FIt comes after widespread reports of
OL,12,Fpatients on trollies, overcrowded
OL,13,Fcubicles and long waits for admission
OL,14,Fand treatment in Northern Ireland's
OL,15,Facute hospitals.
OL,17,FMLAs have called an emergency meeting
OL,18,Fto discuss ongoing pressures on staff
OL,19,Fand patient care.
