OL,7,FConor McCarthy, Unison, highlights
OL,8,Fthat current pressures are "not a
OL,9,Fsurprise".
OL,11,FHe said: "It is completely
OL,12,Funacceptable at the minute with
OL,13,Fregards to patient care.
OL,15,F"Patients being cared for in corridors
OL,16,Fis not what our members signed up for.
OL,18,F"Our wards are packed with patients
OL,19,Fwho should be at home, who should be
OL,20,Fdischarged but they are being cared
OL,21,Ffor on wards.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
