OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,F"Social care is being delivered in
OL,8,Facute hospitals. If we are going to
OL,9,Fchange this, we need real reform in
OL,10,Fsocial care."
OL,12,FStormont's Health Committee will meet
OL,13,Fon Tuesday 7 January. The Minister is
OL,14,Fexpected to provide an update to
OL,15,Fmembers on waiting times.
OL,17,FCommittee Chair Liz Kimmins has said
OL,18,Fthe Executive needs to offer
OL,19,Freassurance to staff and the public
OL,20,Fthat solutions can be found.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
