OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,F"We need to give the public and staff
OL,8,Fconfidence that work is ongoing to try
OL,9,Fand alleviate these pressures.
OL,11,F"We know we cannot fix everything but
OL,12,Fwe want to work collaboratively with
OL,13,Fthem and the Department to find
OL,14,Fsolutions in the short, medium and
OL,15,Flong term to improve and enhance our
OL,16,Fhealth service.
OL,18,F"Patients need to be seen and need to
OL,19,Fbe treated in a timely manner and
OL,20,Fstaff also need to be supported at
OL,21,Fthis really critical time.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
