OL,4,Ccalled to address health service
OL,5,Cpressures
OL,7,F"As a Health Committee, that is our
OL,8,Frole. To scrutinise what is happening,
OL,9,Fwhat work is being done to deal with
OL,10,Fthe issues our health service and
OL,11,Fparticularly our hospitals are facing."
OL,13,FThere is widespread concern that
OL,14,Fmounting pressures will have a
OL,15,Fdevastating impact on staffing levels.
OL,17,F"Morale is at an all-time low. Staff
OL,18,Fare trying their best to care in the
OL,19,Fmost difficult of circumstances.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
